reviewText:
- Good tale;
- Great labyrinths ( though, could use some polishing );
- Great skillsets (not confusing at all ).
-----------------------------------------------
- Some maps are infinite, making you walk... and walk... and walk.. look a cue... no its not... back to walking;
- Magic learning system it's not all that good. Also, some spells have no use for;
- If not by a walkthrough, i would be lost on the last bit of the game.

I see some people giving negative reviews just because is a RPGmaker kinda of game. So please, next time, don't buy a RPGmaker kinda game, if you not play and see the tale through.

